In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=\cos(x)}$, $\blueD{a=-2}$ and $\maroonD{b=7}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{-2}}^{\maroonD 7} \goldD{\cos(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD 7-(\blueD{-2})}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[\sin(x)\Big]_{-2}^7}{9}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\sin(7)-\sin(-2)}{9}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\sin(7)+\sin(2)}{9}
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=\sin(x)}$, $\blueD{a=-6}$ and $\maroonD{b=-1}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{-6}}^{\maroonD {-1}} (\goldD{\sin(x)})\,dx}{\maroonD{-1}-\blueD{(-6)}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[-\cos(x)\Big]_{-6}^{-1}}{5}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{-\cos(-1)-(-\cos(-6))}{5}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\cos(6)-\cos(1)}{5}
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=e^{x}}$, $\blueD{a=3}$ and $\maroonD{b=9}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{3}}^{\maroonD {9}} (\goldD{e^{x}})\,dx}{\maroonD{9}-\blueD{3}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[e^{x}\Big]_{3}^{9}}{6}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{e^{9}-e^{3}}{6}
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=\dfrac{1}{x}}$, $\blueD{a=4}$ and $\maroonD{b=8}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{4}}^{\maroonD {8}} \left(\goldD{\dfrac{1}{x}}\right)\,dx}{\maroonD{8}-\blueD{4}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[\ln|x|\Big]_{4}^{8}}{4}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\ln|8|-\ln|4|}{4}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\ln(2)}{4}
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=\sqrt{x}}$, $\blueD{a=5}$ and $\maroonD{b=12}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{5}}^{\maroonD {12}} (\goldD{\sqrt{x}})\,dx}{\maroonD{12}-\blueD{5}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\left[\dfrac{2\cdot x^{^{\frac{3}{2}}}}{3}\right]_{5}^{12}}{7}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\dfrac{2\cdot 12^{^{\frac{3}{2}}}}{3}-\dfrac{2\cdot 5^{^{\frac{3}{2}}}}{3}}{7}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{2}{21}\cdot (\sqrt{12^3}-\sqrt{5^3})
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=\sqrt[3]{x}}$, $\blueD{a=-5}$ and $\maroonD{b=9}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{-5}}^{\maroonD {9}} (\goldD{\sqrt[3]{x}})\,dx}{\maroonD{9}-\blueD{(-5)}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\left[\dfrac{3\cdot x^{^{\frac{4}{3}}}}{4}\right]_{-5}^{9}}{14}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\dfrac{3\cdot 9^{^{\frac{4}{3}}}}{4}-\dfrac{3\cdot (-5)^{^{\frac{4}{3}}}}{4}}{14}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{3}{56}\cdot(\sqrt[3]{9^4}-\sqrt[3]{5^4})
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=3x^2+4x}$, $\blueD{a=2}$ and $\maroonD{b=6}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{2}}^{\maroonD 6} (\goldD{3x^2+4x})\,dx}{\maroonD 6-\blueD{2}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[x^3+2x^2\Big]_{2}^6}{4}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{288-16}{4}
\\\\
&=68
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=6x^2+8}$, $\blueD{a=3}$ and $\maroonD{b=5}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{3}}^{\maroonD {5}} (\goldD{6x^2+8})\,dx}{\maroonD{5}-\blueD{3}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[2x^3+8x\Big]_{3}^{5}}{2}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{290-78}{2}
\\\\
&=106
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=x^3-9x}$, $\blueD{a=-1}$ and $\maroonD{b=3}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{-1}}^{\maroonD {3}} (\goldD{x^3-9x})\,dx}{\maroonD{3}-\blueD{(-1)}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\left[\dfrac{x^4}{4}-\dfrac{9x^2}{2}\right]_{-1}^{3}}{4}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{-20.25-(-4.25)}{4}
\\\\
&=-4
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=8-2x^3}$, $\blueD{a=2}$ and $\maroonD{b=4}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{2}}^{\maroonD {4}} (\goldD{8-2x^3})\,dx}{\maroonD{4}-\blueD{2}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\left[8x-\dfrac{x^4}{2}\right]_{2}^{4}}{2}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{-96-8}{2}
\\\\
&=-52
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=14-6x^2}$, $\blueD{a=-1}$ and $\maroonD{b=3}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{-1}}^{\maroonD {3}} (\goldD{14-6x^2})\,dx}{\maroonD{3}-\blueD{(-1)}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[14x-2x^3\Big]_{-1}^{3}}{4}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{-12-(-12)}{4}
\\\\
&=0
\end{align}$

In our case, $\goldD{f(x)=-x^2+3}$, $\blueD{a=0}$ and $\maroonD{b=6}$:

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD a}^{\maroonD b} \goldD{f(x)}\,dx}{\maroonD b-\blueD a}&=\dfrac{\displaystyle\int_{\blueD{0}}^{\maroonD {6}} (\goldD{-x^2+3})\,dx}{\maroonD{6}-\blueD{0}}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\Big[-\dfrac{x^3}{3}+3x\Big]_{0}^{6}}{6}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{-54-0}{6}
\\\\
&=-9
\end{align}$
